<inglise> COUNCIL DECISION of 25 February 1991 establishing a Committee on monetary, financial and balance of payments statistics (91/115/EEC) </inglise>
<eesti> N&Otilde;UKOGU OTSUS, millega moodustatakse rahandus-, finantseerimis- ja maksebilansistatistika komitee 25. veebruar 1991 (91/115/EM&Uuml;) </eesti>
<inglise> THE COUNCIL OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE N&Otilde;UKOGU, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the draft decision submitted by the Commission (1), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse komisjoni esitatud otsuse projekti, (1) </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the opinion of the European Parliament (2), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Parlamendi arvamust (2), </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the opinion of the Economic and Social Committee (3), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse majandus- ja sotsiaalkomitee arvamust, (3) </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Council Decision 90/141/EEC of 12 March 1990 on the attainment of progressive convergence of economic policies and performance during stage one of economic and monetary union (4) entails the need for the availability of consistent indicators, particularly in the monetary, financial and balance of payments areas; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: tulenevalt n&otilde;ukogu 12. m&auml;rtsi 1990. aasta otsusest 90/141/EM&Uuml; majanduspoliitika ja majandusliku tulemuslikkuse j&auml;rkj&auml;rgulise l&auml;henemise saavutamise kohta majandus- ja rahaliidu esimesel etapil (1) vajatakse &uuml;htlustatud n&auml;itajaid, eelk&otilde;ige rahanduse, finantseerimise ja maksebilansi alal; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Council Decision 90/142/EEC of 12 March 1990 amending Decision 64/300/EEC on cooperation between the central banks of the Member States of the European Economic Community (5) aims in particular at promoting the coordination of monetary policy which necessarily depends on common surveillance indicators; </inglise>
<eesti> n&otilde;ukogu 12. m&auml;rtsi 1990. aasta otsuse 90/142/EM&Uuml; (millega muudetakse otsust 64/300/EM&Uuml; Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse liikmesriikide keskpankade vahelise koost&ouml;&ouml; kohta) (5) eesm&auml;rk on eelk&otilde;ige edendada rahapoliitika koordineerimist, mis peab tingimata p&otilde;hinema &uuml;histel j&auml;relevalven&auml;itajatel; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas there is therefore a need to establish, as a section of the multiannual statistical programme of the Commission, a multiannual work programme in the field of monetary, financial and balance of payments statistics; </inglise>
<eesti> seet&otilde;ttu on vaja v&auml;lja t&ouml;&ouml;tada komisjoni mitmeaastase statistikaprogrammi &uuml;he osana rahandus-, finantseerimis- ja maksebilansistatistika alane mitmeaastane t&ouml;&ouml;kava; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas by Decision 89/382/EEC, Euratom (6) the Council set up a Committee on the Statistical Programme of the European Communities, comprising representatives of the Member States statistical institutes, to ensure close cooperation between Member States and the Commission whilst the statistical programme is established; </inglise>
<eesti> komisjon moodustas otsusega 89/382/EM&Uuml;, Euratom (6) Euroopa &uuml;henduste statistikaprogrammi komitee, kuhu kuuluvad liikmesriikide statistikaasutuste esindajad, et statistikaprogrammide v&auml;ljat&ouml;&ouml;tamisel tagada tihe koost&ouml;&ouml; liikmesriikide ja komisjoni vahel; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in Member States, monetary and banking statistics are drawn up by central banks, and financial and balance of payments statistics are drawn up by various institutions, including central banks; </inglise>
<eesti> liikmesriikides koostavad rahandus- ja pangandusstatistikat keskpangad ning finantseerimis- ja maksebilansistatistikat erinevad asutused, kaasa arvatud keskpangad; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas there is at present no body which ensures close cooperation between Member States and the Commission in the fields of monetary, financial and balance of payments statistics on which the principal national institutions concerned are represented; </inglise>
<eesti> praegu ei ole asutust, kes tagaks tiheda koost&ouml;&ouml; liikmesriikide ja komisjoni vahel rahandus-, finantseerimis- ja maksebilansistatistika alal ja kus oleksid esindatud peamised asjaomased siseriiklikud asutused; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas it is necessary, in order to achieve such cooperation, in particular with a view to achieving Economic and Monetary Union, to establish a committee composed of representatives of these institutions, which is charged with aiding the Commission in drawing up and implementing the multiannual work programme relating to monetary, financial and balance of payments statistics; </inglise>
<eesti> niisuguse koost&ouml;&ouml; saavutamiseks ja eelk&otilde;ige majandus- ja rahaliidu loomiseks tuleks moodustada nende asutuste esindajatest koosnev komitee, kelle &uuml;lesanne on abistada komisjoni rahandus-, finantseerimis- ja maksebilansistatistika alase mitmeaastase t&ouml;&ouml;kava koostamisel ja rakendamisel; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, having regard to the specific role played in the Member States by the aforementioned institutions, it is necessary to allow the committee to choose its chairman; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse erirolli, mis eespool nimetatud asutustel liikmesriikides on, tuleb komiteel lubada valida endale president; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas there is, from the point of view of statistics, a close interdependence between the monetary, financial and balance of payments areas on the one hand, and certain other areas of economic statistics on the other hand; </inglise>
<eesti> rahandus-, finantseerimis- ja maksebilansistatistika ning teatavad muud majandusstatistika valdkonnad on omavahel tihedalt seotud; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the increased demand from the Member States and Community institutions for improved statistical information requires the enhancement of cooperation between the users and producers of monetary, financial and balance of payments statistics; </inglise>
<eesti> liikmesriikide ja &uuml;henduse asutuste suurenenud n&otilde;udlus parandatud statistiliste andmete j&auml;rele n&otilde;uab rahandus-, finantseerimis- ja maksebilansistatistika kasutajate ja tootjate vahelise koost&ouml;&ouml; t&otilde;hustamist; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas an examination of whether the Committee's tasks will meet the needs of any future European Central Bank System should be carried out in the framework of the achievement of Economic and Monetary Union, </inglise>
<eesti> majandus- ja rahaliidu loomiseks tuleks uurida, kas komitee &uuml;lesanded vastavad tulevase Euroopa Keskpankade S&uuml;steemi vajadustele, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS DECIDED AS FOLLOWS: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD J&Auml;RGMISE OTSUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> A Committee on Monetary, Financial and Balance of Payments Statistics, hereinafter called'the Committee', is hereby established. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolevaga moodustatakse rahandus-, finantseerimis- ja maksebilansistatistika komitee, edaspidi "komitee". </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> The Committee shall assist the Commission in drawing up and implementing the multiannual programme of work relating to monetary, financial and balance of payments statistics. </inglise>
<eesti> Komitee abistab komisjoni rahandus-, finantseerimis- ja maksebilansistatistika alase mitmeaastase t&ouml;&ouml;kava koostamisel ja rakendamisel. </eesti>
<inglise> The Committee shall, in particular, have the task of expressing opinions on the development and coordination of the monetary, financial and balance of payments statistics required for the policies implemented by the Council, the Commission, and the various committees assisting them. </inglise>
<eesti> Komitee &uuml;lesanne on eelk&otilde;ige esitada arvamusi rahandus-, finantseerimis- ja maksebilansistatistika arengu ja koordineerimise kohta, mida n&otilde;ukogu, komisjon ja neid abistavad mitmesugused komiteed vajavad oma poliitika rakendamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise> The Committee may be asked to express opinions on the links between monetary, financial and balance of payments statistics on the one hand, and certain other economic statistics on the other, in particular those on which national accounts are based. </inglise>
<eesti> Komiteelt v&otilde;idakse paluda esitada arvamusi rahandus-, finantseerimis- ja maksebilansistatistika ja teatava muu, eelk&otilde;ige rahvamajanduse arvepidamise aluseks oleva majandusstatistika vaheliste seoste kohta. </eesti>
<inglise> The work of this Committee will be coordinated with that of the Statistical Programme Committee. </inglise>
<eesti> Selle komitee tegevus viiakse koosk&otilde;lla statistikaprogrammi komitee tegevusega. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> The Commission, on its own initiative, and, should the occasion arise, following a request from the Council or from the committees which assist them, shall consult the Committee on: </inglise>
<eesti> Komisjon konsulteerib komiteega omal algatusel v&otilde;i vajaduse korral n&otilde;ukogu v&otilde;i teda abistavate komiteede taotlusel j&auml;rgmistes k&uuml;simustes: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) the establishment of multiannual Community programmes for monetary, financial and balance of payments statistics; </inglise>
<eesti> a) &uuml;henduse rahandus-, finantseerimis- ja maksebilansistatistika alaste mitmeaastaste programmide v&auml;ljat&ouml;&ouml;tamine; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) the measures which the Commission intends to undertake to achieve the objectives referred to in the multiannual programmes for monetary, financial and balance of payments statistics and the resources and timetables involved; </inglise>
<eesti> b) meetmed, mida komisjon kavatseb rakendada rahandus-, finantseerimis- ja maksebilansistatistikaalaste mitmeaastaste programmide eesm&auml;rkide saavutamiseks, ja nende meetmetega seotud vahendid ja ajakavad; </eesti>
<inglise> (c) any other question, in particular questions of methodology, arising from the establishment or implementation of the Statistical Programme in the relevant fields. </inglise>
<eesti> c) muud vastavate valdkondade statistikaprogrammide v&auml;ljat&ouml;&ouml;tamise ja rakendamisega, eelk&otilde;ige kasutatavate meetoditega seotud k&uuml;simused. </eesti>
<inglise> The Committee may express opinions on its own initiative on any questions relating to the establishment or the implementation of statistical programmes in the monetary, financial and balance of payments fields. </inglise>
<eesti> Komitee v&otilde;ib omal algatusel esitada arvamusi k&otilde;ikide k&uuml;simuste kohta, mis on seotud rahandus-, finantseerimis- ja maksebilansialaste statistikaprogrammide v&auml;ljat&ouml;&ouml;tamise v&otilde;i rakendamisega. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 4 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 4 </eesti>
<inglise> The Committee shall be composed of one, two or three representatives per Member State, coming from the institutions principally concerned with financial, monetary and balance of payments statistics, and of three representatives of the Commission. </inglise>
<eesti> Komitee koosneb &uuml;hest kuni kolmest esindajast liikmesriigi kohta, kes tulevad k&otilde;ige t&auml;htsamates rahandus-, finantseerimis- ja maksebilansistatistikaga tegelevatest asutustest, ning kolmest komisjoni esindajast. </eesti>
<inglise> In addition, one representative of the Committee of Governors of the Central Banks of the Community and one representative of the Monetary Committee may attend meetings of the Committee as observers. </inglise>
<eesti> Lisaks nendele v&otilde;ib komitee koosolekutest vaatlejana osa v&otilde;tta &uuml;ks &uuml;henduse keskpankade juhatajate komitee liige ja &uuml;ks valuutakomitee liige. </eesti>
<inglise> Representatives of other organizations, as well as any persons able to contribute to discussions, may, on the decision of the Committee, participate in the Committee's meetings. </inglise>
<eesti> Muude organisatsioonide esindajad ja k&otilde;ik isikud, kelle osalemine aruteludel on p&otilde;hjendatud, v&otilde;ivad komitee otsusega komitee koosolekutel osaleda. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 5 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 5 </eesti>
<inglise> The Committee shall elect its chairman by a simple majority of the Member States' votes. </inglise>
<eesti> Komitee valib oma presidendi liikmesriikide lihth&auml;&auml;lteenamusega. </eesti>
<inglise> Its secretariat shall be provided by the Commission. </inglise>
<eesti> Sekretariaadi osakonna eest hoolitseb komisjon. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 6 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 6 Komitee koostab oma t&ouml;&ouml;korra. </eesti>
<inglise> The Committee shall draw up its rules of procedure. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 25. veebruar 1991 N&otilde;ukogu nimel </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 25 February 1991. </inglise>
